whatever are you doing here?

1934
02:09:12,704 --> 02:09:14,754
Nothing.
I spend most of my nights here.

1935
02:09:14,956 --> 02:09:18,166
It's the only place where I'm happy.
Don't laugh at me, Miss Doolittle.

1936
02:09:18,376 --> 02:09:20,336
