1938
02:09:24,340 --> 02:09:27,970
Oh, Freddy, you don't think
I'm a heartless guttersnipe, do you?

1939
02:09:28,178 --> 02:09:31,218
Darling, how could you imagine
such a thing? You know how I feel.

1940
02:09:31,431 --> 02:09:34,311
