1961
02:10:44,546 --> 02:10:50,046
Show me now

1962
02:10:51,177 --> 02:10:54,217
Sing me no song
Read me no rhyme

1963
02:10:54,430 --> 02:10:58,100
Don't waste my time
Show me

1964
02:10:58,309 --> 02:11:01,139
